- We just have to eat this?

164
00:04:53,994 --> 00:04:55,230
- Wait, there's more.
- What's going on?

165
00:04:55,254 --> 00:04:56,894
- This is weird.
- Hey. Something is off.

166
00:04:57,164 --> 00:04:58,293
(What's going on?)

167
00:04:58,294 --> 00:05:00,133
(Hey. Something is off.)

168
00:05:00,134 --> 00:05:01,334
