254
00:07:44,124 --> 00:07:46,494
(they must finish everything and leave no food behind.)

255
00:07:46,894 --> 00:07:48,033
Mine was the fried dumpling.

256
00:07:48,034 --> 00:07:49,464
Ki Taek. You...

257
00:07:49,634 --> 00:07:50,963
